# Creating a Beautiful Static Landing Page for Salate Mustaqeem

Yes, I can help you create a beautiful static landing page for your Salate Mustaqeem app. I'll provide you with the
HTML, CSS, and JavaScript code that you can host anywhere (GitHub Pages, Vercel, Netlify, etc.).

Here's a complete landing page design that highlights the features of your prayer app:

## HTML Code (index.html)

