        (hero-mockup.png) 3. **Screenshots**: 5 screenshots of different features in your app (screenshot-1.png through
        screenshot-5.png) You can generate these images using tools like: - Mockup generators (e.g., Shotbot, AppMockUp)
        - Screenshot editing tools (e.g., Figma, Photoshop) - Or use actual screenshots from your app with some light
        editing ## Hosting Your Landing Page 1. **GitHub Pages** (Free): - Create a repository - Upload these files -
