        ## Notes About This Privacy Policy

        1. **Comprehensiveness**: This privacy policy covers all the permissions your app requests (location, calendar,
        media library, microphone, speech recognition) and explains why each is needed.

        2. **Mobile App Focus**: The policy is specifically crafted for a mobile application rather than a general
        website.

        3. **User-Friendly Format**: Information is organized in clear sections with a clean, readable design.

        4. **Legal Compliance**: Includes sections on data rights, children's privacy, and other elements required by
        regulations like GDPR and CCPA.

        5. **Integration with Your Site**: The page matches your main site's design and includes navigation back to the
        main pages.

        ## Implementation Instructions

        1. Save this file as `privacy-policy.html` in your website's root directory (same location as your index.html
        file).

        2. Make sure to update the contact email (`support@imuslimlife.com`) and contact page URL to your actual contact
        information.

        3. You should also create a link to this privacy policy page in the footer of your index.html file by updating
        the link in the "Legal" section:
        ```html
        <li><a href="privacy-policy.html">Privacy Policy</a></li>
        ```

        4. Consider creating a similar "Terms of Service" page if your app requires one.

        5. Update the "Last Updated" date whenever you make significant changes to your privacy policy.

        This privacy policy should satisfy most app store requirements for privacy disclosures and provide transparency
        to your users about how their data is handled.

